T: When all this was finished, all Israel who were present went out to the cities of Judah, and they broke the pillars in pieces, and they cut down the Asherah wooden images, and they broke down the high places and the altars from all Judah and Benjamin and Ephraim and Manasseh, until to finish. And all the sons of Israel returned, every man to his possession, to their own cities. 


